Installation
------------

x86_64:
------

sudo apt-get install git

git clone https://github.com/mirabitl/SDHCAL.git

cd SDHCAl

source  wheezy_install

#if DB is needed (lyosvn password needed)

source dbinstall 

# Then installation of DAQ code 
cd SDHCAL
./install


arm:
---

Just skip the DB installation (Oracle driver not supported)

Remarks:
--------

For DIM daq configuration, configuration and daemon must be copied from 
SDHCAL/DimCtrl/etc and modified according to your setup


